# M0 — Passthrough proxy skeleton (Anthropic mode)

**Date:** 2026-06-30
**Sprint label:** NEW
**Default labels:** enhancement, backend
**Status:** drafted

Milestone M0 of claude-proxy: stand up a local FastAPI proxy on
`127.0.0.1:8788` that **transparently relays** Claude Code's API calls to
`https://api.anthropic.com`, forwarding the caller's own auth/version headers
**byte-for-byte**. Transparency is the entire point of this milestone: because
the proxy never touches the body or the auth header, whatever login Claude Code
holds — a Pro/Max **subscription** OAuth bearer or an API key — reaches Anthropic
unchanged, so `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8788 claude -p "hi"` behaves
identically to talking to Anthropic directly. This also lays the routing/forward
foundation that M1+ extend.

